rows.LABEL: Errors
rows.DATA_ADDRESS: IFNULL((SELECT SUM([#~alias#]ts.diffs_in_message_flag+[#~alias#]ts.diffs_in_result_flag+[#~alias#]ts.diffs_in_output_flag) FROM exf_actest_test_step [#~alias#]ts WHERE [#~alias#]ts.test_case_oid = [#~alias#].oid GROUP BY [#~alias#]ts.test_case_oid),0)

rows.LABEL: Ignore result differences
rows.SHORT_DESCRIPTION: Makes the test step only check for exceptions, no check for differences in the actual result. This is usefull for reading volatile data, that would always change anyway.
